#### CREDENTIAL AUTHENTICATE => /datavice/v1/user/auth

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=un (value=Username), key=pw (value=Password)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Authentication Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Unknown username. Check again or try your email address.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: '<strong>ERROR</strong>: The password you entered for the username <strong>USERNAME HERE</strong> is incorrect. <a href=\"http://localhost/wp-login.php?action=lostpassword\">Lost your password?</a>' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "data": {
            "wpid": 1,
            "snky": "daMjLapFixr6olYJbyYcWPYssHcV7oNdHkM6HfDdHaI"
        }
    }
```

#### Verification => /datavice/v1/user/verify

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=wpid (value=User ID), key=snky (value=Session Key)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Token Not Found!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Token Expired!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. User Not Found!' data: null


IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success"
    }
```

#### FORGOTTEN OR LOST PASSWORD => /datavice/v1/user/forgot

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=UN (value=Username or Email)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Email or username doesn't exists!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password reset is ongoing. Wait for 30 minutes then try again.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password reset key failed to updated.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact site administrator. Email not sent!' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "An email has been sent to your email address."
    }
```

#### CHANGE PASSWORD => /datavice/v1/user/reset

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=ak (value=Activation Key), key=un (value=Username or Email), key=pw (value=New Password)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Username or email does not exists!.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password reset key and username/email is invalid!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password reset key is already used.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password reset key is already expired.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Password was not change.' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Password updated successfully!"
    }
```

#### SIGN UP => /datavice/v1/user/signup
REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=un (value=username), key=em (value=email), key=fn (value=first_name), key=ln (value=last_name), key=gd (value=gender), key=bd (value=birthday), key=co (value=country id), key=province (value=province id), key=ct (value=city id), key=bg (value=barangay id)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Username or Email already exists' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid value for gender.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid email address.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid birthday format.' data: null

- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid value for country.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Not available yet in selected country.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid value for province.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Not available yet in selected province.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid value for city.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Not available yet in selected city.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Invalid value for barangay.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Not available yet in selected barangay.' data: null
- code: 'error' message: 'An error occured while submitting data to the server.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact site administrator. Email not sent!' data: null
- code: 'error' message: 'WordPress Error!' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
       "status" => "success",
       "message" => "Please check your email for password reset key.",
    }
```

#### PROFILE => /datavice/v1/user/profile
REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=wpid (value=User ID), key=snky (value=Session Key)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Token Not Found!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Token Expired!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. User Not Found!' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "data": {
            "uname": "demoguy",
            "dname": "Demo Goodguy",
            "email": "devops@pasabuy.app",
